[ Christmas laughing ]

938
01:01:47,101 --> 01:01:49,069
WARD: But I feel
like a hunter

939
01:01:49,071 --> 01:01:51,004
with two coveys
flushed at once!

940
01:01:51,006 --> 01:01:53,506
[ laughter ]

941
01:01:57,244 --> 01:02:02,549
So, I ask you,
which way do I shoot?

942
01:02:02,551 --> 01:02:05,852
Well, not at your fellow
hunter, for God's sake.

943
01:02:05,854 --> 01:02:07,287
[ laughter ]

944
01:02:11,525 --> 01:02:13,360
What'd you say?

945
01:02:14,161 --> 01:02:15,795
What'd you say?

946
01:02:18,032 --> 01:02:19,733
[ laughter ]

947
01:02:19,735 --> 01:02:23,603
Then at the city bird that
created this abominable law?

948
01:02:23,605 --> 01:02:26,740
Why, his
is but empty bravado,

949
01:02:26,742 --> 01:02:28,641
amateur posturing.

950
01:02:28,643 --> 01:02:30,643
A creature
with duck's feet,

951
01:02:30,645 --> 01:02:34,447
snake's heart
and an ass's disposition.

952
01:02:34,449 --> 01:02:37,283
[ shouts of agreement ]

953
01:02:37,285 --> 01:02:40,086
No!

954
01:02:40,088 --> 01:02:43,857
It is
our country cousin who,

955
01:02:43,859 --> 01:02:47,560
by failing to be conscientious
in the use of his gun,

956
01:02:47,562 --> 01:02:53,533
has made our city cousin
write this dreaded law.

957
01:02:56,103 --> 01:02:59,305
[ laughter ]

958
01:03:00,941 --> 01:03:02,842
Aye, aye, aye!

959
01:03:02,844 --> 01:03:04,978
[ laughing ]

960
01:03:06,947 --> 01:03:08,915
Doodly do.

961
01:03:09,984 --> 01:03:14,287
Hello, Miss Lucy.

962
01:03:14,289 --> 01:03:16,689
LUCY: Whatever it is you
think you're hidin' from...

963
01:03:16,691 --> 01:03:18,525
[ laughing ]

964
01:03:18,527 --> 01:03:21,461
I'm doin'
no such thing.

965
01:03:21,463 --> 01:03:23,463
You know exactly
where to find me.

966
01:03:23,465 --> 01:03:25,131
I don't mean from me.

967
01:03:25,133 --> 01:03:27,000
What, then?

968
01:03:27,002 --> 01:03:28,768
I see you, Ward Allen.

969
01:03:28,770 --> 01:03:30,470
I see what you're
capable of,

970
01:03:30,472 --> 01:03:32,238
and I see how far
you've missed the mark.

971
01:03:32,240 --> 01:03:35,675
Sweetheart, you questioning
my marksmanship?

972
01:03:35,677 --> 01:03:37,744
LUCY:
I question your choices,

973
01:03:37,746 --> 01:03:40,413
especially the ones
that will send you to an early grave.

974
01:03:40,415 --> 01:03:43,016
Woman, you'd have me
your lap dog,

975
01:03:43,018 --> 01:03:46,553
sittin' at your heels,
fetchin' at your command.

976
01:03:46,555 --> 01:03:47,954
Well, I tell you what,
little lady,

977
01:03:47,956 --> 01:03:51,224
even a retriever
must have its own instincts,

978
01:03:51,226 --> 01:03:52,792
act on its own accord,

979
01:03:52,794 --> 01:03:54,327
if it's to be worth
its salt.

980
01:03:54,329 --> 01:03:56,729
Oh, apropos you would
liken yourself to a dog.

981
01:03:56,731 --> 01:03:59,265
Woof!
I am my own master.

982
01:03:59,267 --> 01:04:01,401
Leave me be, woman.

983
01:04:01,403 --> 01:04:02,969
Never.

984
01:04:02,971 --> 01:04:05,705
You will if I say so.

985
01:04:05,707 --> 01:04:07,607
So you'll shoot me?

986
01:04:11,178 --> 01:04:13,413
[ gasping ]

987
01:04:17,751 --> 01:04:19,185
See me now?

988
01:04:19,187 --> 01:04:21,421
[ laughing ]

989
01:04:21,423 --> 01:04:22,822
[ thud, Ward groans ]

990
01:04:22,824 --> 01:04:24,557
WARD: By the plaintiff's
own admission,

991
01:04:24,559 --> 01:04:27,427
on the day in question,

992
01:04:27,429 --> 01:04:30,230
and by her own
eyewitness account,

993
01:04:30,232 --> 01:04:33,032
she has established it was I

994
01:04:33,034 --> 01:04:36,503
that shot out cleanly
the eyes of this portrait

995
01:04:36,505 --> 01:04:39,939
from a distance
of no less than...

996
01:04:39,941 --> 01:04:42,108
[ whistling ]

997
01:04:43,944 --> 01:04:45,545
15 paces,

998
01:04:45,547 --> 01:04:48,781
our parlor being
the largest room in the house.

999
01:04:48,783 --> 01:04:50,683
[ laughter ]

1000
01:04:50,685 --> 01:04:52,752
There are many tests

1001
01:04:52,754 --> 01:04:54,821
of a man's
relative sobriety.

1002
01:04:54,823 --> 01:04:56,122
[ laughter ]

1003
01:04:56,124 --> 01:04:58,258
And I offer to you that
such a piece of marksmanship

1004
01:04:58,260 --> 01:05:00,460
belongs among those tests.

1005
01:05:00,462 --> 01:05:02,962
It can
only be deduced then

1006
01:05:02,964 --> 01:05:05,365
that the esteemed lady
is incorrect

1007
01:05:05,367 --> 01:05:08,268
in one statement
or the other.

1008
01:05:08,270 --> 01:05:10,303
Either I was drunk... Whoo!

1009
01:05:10,305 --> 01:05:11,971
[ laughter ]

1010
01:05:11,973 --> 01:05:14,674
Or I made these shots.

1011
01:05:18,145 --> 01:05:19,646
But most certainly...

1012
01:05:19,648 --> 01:05:24,317
Most certainly,
the two statements stand

1013
01:05:24,319 --> 01:05:27,387
as mutually
incompatible assertions.

1014
01:05:27,389 --> 01:05:29,022
This is ridiculous!

1015
01:05:29,024 --> 01:05:30,957
JUDGE HARDEN:
Mr. Allen, your reputation

1016
01:05:30,959 --> 01:05:33,059
as a marksman
is well established.

1017
01:05:33,061 --> 01:05:36,596
And clearly, I would not have
to bend the law or my judgment

1018
01:05:36,598 --> 01:05:40,967
very far to dismiss the charge
and send you on your way.

1019
01:05:40,969 --> 01:05:42,735
Fancy logic does
not change the truth!

1020
01:05:42,737 --> 01:05:44,070
JUDGE HARDEN: Sit down,
please, Mrs. Allen.

1021
01:05:44,072 --> 01:05:45,705
Get off of me!

1022
01:05:45,707 --> 01:05:49,609
However, I find it
in the interest of public safety

1023
01:05:49,611 --> 01:05:51,010
to call you guilty...

1024
01:05:51,012 --> 01:05:52,412
What?!

1025
01:05:52,414 --> 01:05:53,479
and put you in jail
for 10 days.

1026
01:05:53,481 --> 01:05:54,614
Hear, hear!

1027
01:05:54,616 --> 01:05:55,715
JUDGE HARDEN:
Order. Order.

1028
01:05:55,717 --> 01:05:57,116
This is an atrocity.
Approach.

1029
01:05:57,118 --> 01:05:58,585
Approach now.

1030
01:05:58,587 --> 01:06:00,954
10 days may not be
enough to cool her off.

1031
01:06:00,956 --> 01:06:05,325
If I were you, I would
spend those 10 days

1032
01:06:05,327 --> 01:06:07,860
using my way
with words to conjure up

1033
01:06:07,862 --> 01:06:13,066
one big Kingdom Come
prayer for your salvation.

1034
01:06:13,068 --> 01:06:14,701
[ door slams ]

1035
01:06:32,086 --> 01:06:34,153
[ frustrated sigh ]

1036
01:06:34,155 --> 01:06:35,355
[ groans ]

1037
