have rights.

1270
01:32:12,359 --> 01:32:14,993
John Eliot Ward wrote
that deed himself.

1271
01:32:14,995 --> 01:32:16,561
That ain't
the point, Jack.

1272
01:32:16,563 --> 01:32:20,064
Besides, Christmas can't
even take care of himself.

1273
01:32:20,066 --> 01:32:21,432
He'd probably starve
to death

1274
01:32:21,434 --> 01:32:23,134
if you weren't
feeding him.

1275
01:32:26,772 --> 01:32:28,740
Thought you
were gonna save that

1276
01:32:28,742 --> 01:32:30,375
for a special occasion?

1277
01:32:30,377 --> 01:32:33,845
Well, there's... There's
nothing as special

1278
01:32:33,847 --> 01:32:35,513
as the present, Roy.

1279
01:32:40,286 --> 01:32:42,720
Let me ask you something.

1280
01:32:42,722 --> 01:32:47,225
You ever stop and listen
to the words of the old Negro songs?

1281
01:32:47,227 --> 01:32:49,494
Can't understand
